1
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:38,289
[Too Young To Love]

2
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:41,330
[Episode 3]

3
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:49,780
Zhao Zhenghao!

4
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,039
If you lose,

5
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,410
you must not pick on them again.

6
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,050
But if you guys lose,

7
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,120
you have to apologize to us
at the school gate.

8
00:01:58,120 --> 00:02:00,120
I'll have everyone in the school know

9
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,720
who's the toughest guy here.

10
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:02,800
Two on two.

11
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:03,930
Let's begin.

12
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:16,530
Why are they playing basketball here?

13
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:19,740
I heard they fought over drinks
at the vending machine.

14
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,480
I bought that!

15
00:02:38,180 --> 00:02:40,850
[Men's Room]

16
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,590
That's not it. They bumped into each other

17
00:02:39,590 --> 00:02:42,720
in the washroom, quarreled,
and nearly got into a fight.

18
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,120
Hey!

19
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,540
I've had enough of you.

20
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:52,240
Just because you have good grades
doesn't mean I dare not beat you.

21
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,360
Zhao Zhenghao, the school rules say

22
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:55,360
brawling can be a ground for expulsion.

23
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:57,000
Since you're asking for trouble,

24
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,000
then act like a man

25
00:02:58,079 --> 00:02:59,560
and have a fair fight with me.

26
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,150
Sure. Let's do it in the P.E. class.

27
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:01,950
It's settled.

28
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,680
See you on the playground.

29
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,000
Hope you won't chicken out.

30
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,130
Or I'll despise you.

31
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:09,430
Unlike some people,
I don't take advantage

32
00:03:09,590 --> 00:03:11,560
of those taking a bathroom break.

33
00:03:13,590 --> 00:03:15,590
Zhenghao, calm down.

34
00:03:17,930 --> 00:03:22,020
[Men's Room]

35
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:24,800
What exactly are they up to?

36
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,800
Zhao Zhenghao is amazing!

37
00:03:43,430 --> 00:03:45,000
Whose side are you on?

38
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:47,180
I'm on Tong Xiaole's side, of course.

39
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,570
I didn't touch him.
He just fell on his own!

40
00:03:59,079 --> 00:04:01,280
Sir, I think I have a fractured bone.

41
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:03,800
Eyes front!

42
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,530
As fellow students,

43
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,400
you should be kind and supportive

44
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,150
to each other.

45
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:10,880
How could you fight each other?

46
00:04:12,430 --> 00:04:13,490
Here's what you do.

47
00:04:13,870 --> 00:04:14,930
Stand face to face,

48
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:15,710
hold your hands,

49
00:04:15,710 --> 00:04:17,720
and name five of each other's strengths.

50
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,579
Zhao Zhenghao,

51
00:04:18,950 --> 00:04:19,680
you go first.

52
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,690
What are you staring at?

53
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,920
You have good grades.

54
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,040
So what?

55
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,740
You're good-looking.

56
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:44,600
So what?

57
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,060
You play basketball well,

58
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,600
but I'm still better.

59
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:51,920
As for height...

60
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,659
you're roughly as tall as I am.

61
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,240
All the teachers like you.

62
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,000
I'm done, Sir.

63
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:02,250
It's your turn.

64
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:04,920
Yes, Sir.

65
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,720
Zhao Zhenghao...

66
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:10,620
is fairly responsible and generous.

67
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,720
He never bullies others

68
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,250
or loses his temper easily.

69
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:17,040
As the captain of the school orchestra,

70
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,370
he's highly competent.

71
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,880
Alright, that's enough.

72
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,180
The floor is yours now.

73
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,600
I suggest we take turns to name

74
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,940
one strength at a time.

75
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,000
Okay.

76
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,920
You have beautiful eyes.

77
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:44,050
Your nose is the best part of your face.

78
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:48,240
Your hair is flowy, though thinning.

79
00:05:48,270 --> 00:05:49,390
Your ears look fine

80
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,040
from the front,

81
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:53,300
though they indicate you're a pushover.

82
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:57,570
Why am I the first one to speak
at each turn?

83
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:01,240
You have broad shoulders.

84
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,600
Your eyes aren't pretty,

85
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,920
but you have great eyesight.

86
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,780
You're endowed with a deep voice,

87
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,200
but it's unpleasant.

88
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,160
You are friends with the top student.

89
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:13,020
You play basketball well.
You can speak quite fast.

90
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,160
There you go.

91
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,130
Alright.

92
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,540
You're dismissed.

93
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:19,130
Go, boys.

94
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:26,480
Zhao Zhenghao.

95
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,600
If you ever bully them again,

96
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:32,130
I'll treat you like this...

97
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,920
Sir, Zhao Zhenghao just hit me!

98
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,159
I'm in pain!

99
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:41,020
Zhao Zhenghao!

100
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:44,360
Did he really hit you?

101
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:45,720
Did he?

102
00:06:45,830 --> 00:06:47,430
I need to go to the infirmary.

103
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,620
On your best behavior!

104
00:07:00,900 --> 00:07:02,410
[Class 9, Grade 11]

105
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,720
The results of the monthly exam are in.

106
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,690
I'll give each of you
your test paper back.

107
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,270
Look what you did wrong.

108
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:12,270
You could've gotten points
by writing one more line in the answers,

109
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,530
but you just wouldn't.

110
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,380
Listen,

111
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,920
it is still Tong Xiaole
who has the highest score.

112
00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:19,320
[Qingmu High School Monthly Test
for Grade 11 Students]

113
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,090
The lowest score

114
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:19,920
is 48.

115
00:07:20,650 --> 00:07:21,960
[Name: Luo Ningzi] [Score: 138]

116
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:23,240
As for who took it, I won't say.

117
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,800
Just see for yourselves,

118
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:26,800
as each of you will have your paper back.

119
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:28,330
Take out your mistake logs.

120
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,560
Write down the questions

121
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,730
you answered wrong.

122
00:07:31,860 --> 00:07:34,180
[Qingmu High School Monthly Test
for Grade 11 Students] [Score: 48]

123
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:32,800
As I said before,

124
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,510
good grades are within reach,

125
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:36,750
as long as you put in

126
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,720
some real effort.

127
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:47,040
Why haven't they come back
from the infirmary?

128
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,270
Are they in trouble?

129
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,830
Tong Xiaole!

130
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,750
Tong Xiaole!

131
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,920
My goodness.

132
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,480
Is it that serious?

133
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,360
Are you okay?

134
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:11,830
It's you, Yi Lan.

135
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,270
I thought you were faking it.

136
00:08:14,270 --> 00:08:15,870
Little did I know it was real.

137
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,680
Get up now.

138
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:22,300
Isn't a self-study class in session?

139
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:25,220
Are you sure
coming here won't affect your studies?

140
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:27,720
Is your head hurting?

141
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,120
Yes.

142
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,360
What about other places?

143
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,600
Are you hurt anywhere else?

144
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,480
How about your legs?

145
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,409
My legs are fine.

146
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,720
Oh my god.

147
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,340
Has this wound been disinfected?

148
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,150
Not yet.

149
00:08:40,030 --> 00:08:42,030
The school nurse is on leave today,

150
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:43,690
so it hasn't been attended to.

151
00:08:43,909 --> 00:08:44,600
Yi Lan,

152
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,790
this wound is actually no big deal.

153
00:08:48,510 --> 00:08:51,570
It must be disinfected
to prevent infection, you know?

154
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,000
I'm fine.

155
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,200
Does it hurt?

156
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:58,960
Yes, terribly.

157
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,240
Just bear with it.

158
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,080
How about...

159
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:04,360
you

160
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:06,520
blow on my wound to ease the pain?

161
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,080
Okay.

162
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,620
I think that will work.

163
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,450
Are you feeling better?

164
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,850
Y-Yes, much better.

165
00:09:35,750 --> 00:09:36,750
Let me put this on.

166
00:09:43,510 --> 00:09:45,360
How are you going to do homework then?

167
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,620
Can you move this hand?

168
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,280
Is it hurting?

169
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:55,870
Luo Ningzi.

170
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:56,720
Ning.

171
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:58,960
Where is Chen Fan?

172
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,960
Where is Chen Fan?

173
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,480
I'm right here!

174
00:10:03,630 --> 00:10:05,750
I heard everything,

175
00:10:05,750 --> 00:10:09,000
including
"blow on my wound to ease the pain."

176
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,570
God knows what has got into him.

177
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:17,560
I won't wait for you after school today.

178
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,930
Don't go so fast! Isn't your head hurting?

179
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,600
Looks like you're fine.

180
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,690
Are you okay?

181
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:31,160
I'm in perfect condition. Don't worry.

182
00:10:31,750 --> 00:10:33,630
Zhao Zhenghao won't bother you anymore.

183
00:10:33,630 --> 00:10:35,360
Thanks for everything you did.

184
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:36,960
Don't mention it.

185
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,840
If Zhao Zhenghao ever troubles you again,

186
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,360
I will...

187
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:40,720
kick him away.

188
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,170
I'm going back to study.

189
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:51,440
Boss!

190
00:10:51,870 --> 00:10:52,600
Boss!

191
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:56,480
My boss...

192
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,120
Are you alright?

193
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,560
What took you so long?

194
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:04,360
I would've come earlier if the teacher
hadn't made me stay for papers.

195
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,720
I'm sorry, Boss...

196
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:10,240
G-Go back to your papers. Leave me alone.

197
00:11:10,510 --> 00:11:11,320
Boss,

198
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,840
you're more important than papers.

199
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:19,870
Chen Fan and Tong Xiaole
went way out of line.

200
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:22,410
Shall we teach them a lesson again?

201
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:25,210
Don't you see my leg's injured?

202
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,600
If it worsens,
serious problems will occur.

203
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,440
Yes. Your leg needs proper care.

204
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,440
Let me rub it.

205
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,000
Nice skills.

206
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,120
Of course.

207
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,650
Give me a second.

208
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:43,590
It's quite a steep slope.

209
00:11:43,750 --> 00:11:45,080
Are you up for this?

210
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,430
Yes, yes. I got it.

211
00:11:58,390 --> 00:11:59,720
Yi Lan, why not let me ride it instead?

212
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:00,630
No, no, no.

213
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:03,200
What if you fall and break your brain?

214
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:05,510
That precious brain of yours
is for studying.

215
00:12:05,510 --> 00:12:07,840
Leave this manual labor to me.

216
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:24,250
Anything wrong?

217
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,720
I-I can walk home myself.

218
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:26,720
But why?

219
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:28,750
I can give you a ride!

220
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,000
Sit down.

221
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,480
I'll cook for you.

222
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:42,510
There's no food in the fridge.

223
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,750
It really is empty.

224
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:48,800
But it's fine.

225
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,760
I'll shop for groceries.

226
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,160
I've got this.

227
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:55,240
Yi Lan.

228
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,080
Yi Lan!

229
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:58,720
Why...

230
00:12:58,870 --> 00:13:00,320
why don't we go out to eat?

231
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:02,840
These shrimps...

232
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:05,510
really died a terrible death.

233
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:10,200
It's true that they don't look good,

234
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:12,720
but I'm sure they taste fine.

235
00:13:14,870 --> 00:13:15,360
Okay.

236
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:23,850
Is this stir fried tomatoes with eggs?

237
00:13:24,510 --> 00:13:24,870
Yes.

238
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:26,440
Just taste it.

239
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:29,050
Are you sure
I won't end up in the hospital?

240
00:13:46,870 --> 00:13:47,960
It's actually good.

241
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:48,360
Really?

242
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,870
Ugly though it seems,

243
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:50,650
it tastes

244
00:13:50,870 --> 00:13:51,750
unexpectedly good.

245
00:13:51,750 --> 00:13:52,360
Yeah.

246
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,800
So you didn't taste it after cooking it?

247
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:56,840
I stir fried it for a second time.

248
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,300
Now it tastes even better.

249
00:14:01,870 --> 00:14:02,440
Yi Lan.

250
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:05,490
I want some shrimps.

251
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:12,780
But I don't think I can peel them
with this injured hand.

252
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:16,680
You're well. Your mouth is not injured.

253
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:21,840
Fine.

254
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:26,290
Time to confess.

255
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:28,120
Why are you suddenly being so nice to me?

256
00:14:28,120 --> 00:14:30,240
One who is unaccountably solicitous
must have evil intentions.

257
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:31,000
What do you want?

258
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:32,530
What could I possibly want?

259
00:14:32,550 --> 00:14:34,550
I saw you all by yourself with nobody

260
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,180
attending to your injury.

261
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:39,240
I felt the need to take care of you
since we're best friends.

262
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:40,700
Isn't your best friend...

263
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,750
Luo Ningzi?

264
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:45,000
Luo Ningzi is a good friend of mine.

265
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,240
You are my best friend.

266
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,900
That can't be the same, right?

267
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:50,360
It actually sounds... sincere.

268
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:52,120
But I don't buy it.

269
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:54,440
I was worried sick about you,

270
00:14:54,440 --> 00:14:56,080
so I visited you at the infirmary.

271
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:58,240
How can you be so ungrateful?

272
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,480
I just made you a feast.

273
00:15:04,860 --> 00:15:06,250
[Qingmu High School Monthly Test
for Grade 11 Students] [Score: 48]

274
00:15:08,820 --> 00:15:09,420
[Qingmu High School Monthly Test
for Grade 11 Students]

275
00:15:09,450 --> 00:15:12,080
This low score is a real shame.
Why bring my paper out?

276
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:13,510
But I don't think it's a shame.

277
00:15:13,510 --> 00:15:14,840
On the contrary, I'm proud of it.

278
00:15:14,840 --> 00:15:15,790
You got 10 last time,

279
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:17,590
and 48 this time. It's progress.

280
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:19,120
Stop mocking me.

281
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:21,480
Even the way Luo Ningzi looks at me
has changed.

282
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,720
Finals are coming up soon.

283
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:24,120
Could you please help me?

284
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:27,240
You have a knack for taking exams, Xiaole.

285
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:29,480
And I'm your best friend.

286
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:31,780
Just help me pass the finals, please.

287
00:15:33,750 --> 00:15:34,720
Look at my eyes.

288
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:37,600
You already did a great job.

289
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:39,000
You were really close to passing.

290
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,240
It was an achievement itself.

291
00:15:40,240 --> 00:15:41,630
Are you my best friend or not?

292
00:15:41,630 --> 00:15:43,320
Will you help me? Yes or no?

293
00:15:43,630 --> 00:15:45,120
Now, cancel these two out

294
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:46,600
to get this equation.

295
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:48,200
Alright, that's about it.

296
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:50,800
Next, just recite the text
of Hongmen Banquet.

297
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:55,530
♪ She left in spring ♪

298
00:15:56,460 --> 00:15:59,340
♪ Gone with her was cherry blossoms ♪

299
00:16:00,050 --> 00:16:02,470
♪ On the once youthful face ♪

300
00:16:03,660 --> 00:16:06,340
♪ There were tears amidst confusion ♪

301
00:16:07,220 --> 00:16:09,490
♪ She left in spring ♪

302
00:16:10,590 --> 00:16:13,170
♪ All was like a dream ♪

303
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:15,240
That's enough studying.

304
00:16:13,940 --> 00:16:16,710
♪ Youth never lasts ♪

305
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,120
Go to bed now.

306
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:19,750
Sure, just after I finish this, Dad.

307
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:20,650
♪ Just let her go ♪

308
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:22,080
Stop it now.

309
00:16:21,820 --> 00:16:24,010
♪ The paper plane that was once set free ♪

310
00:16:22,750 --> 00:16:23,480
Go to sleep.

311
00:16:24,170 --> 00:16:27,570
♪ Will find its way back
to the old desk and chair at school ♪

312
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,840
Time for a mock exam.

313
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:27,780
Pass the papers to those behind you.

314
00:16:27,780 --> 00:16:30,600
♪ All stories have yet to end ♪

315
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:32,610
♪ Let me write for you ♪

316
00:16:32,670 --> 00:16:36,500
♪ An old CD will witness
our ever-ending dreams ♪

317
00:16:36,610 --> 00:16:39,660
♪ Youth is nothing but a farce ♪

318
00:16:39,750 --> 00:16:42,560
♪ In which everyone has fun till the end ♪

319
00:16:42,690 --> 00:16:46,320
♪ Joy and sorrow are woven together ♪

320
00:16:44,290 --> 00:16:45,820
[Class 9, Grade 11]

321
00:16:46,530 --> 00:16:50,180
♪ Every experience will bring me closer ♪

322
00:16:50,370 --> 00:16:50,970
♪ To myself ♪

323
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:58,360
Tong Xiaole,

324
00:16:58,960 --> 00:16:59,870
you are really something.

325
00:16:59,870 --> 00:17:01,750
Your predictions about the exam
were spot on.

326
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:04,349
I finally passed one exam,
with the score of 91.

327
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:05,829
A breakthrough, finally!

328
00:17:05,829 --> 00:17:07,240
You've been secretly tutoring her?

329
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:08,510
I want to join, Xiaole.

330
00:17:09,069 --> 00:17:10,069
What's with you?

331
00:17:10,069 --> 00:17:11,510
Why didn't you count me in
on that good thing?

332
00:17:11,510 --> 00:17:13,400
Do you not consider me as a close friend?

333
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:14,530
I'd like to join too.

334
00:17:15,720 --> 00:17:17,920
No, no, absolutely not. No way.

335
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:19,440
Now, what does that mean?

336
00:17:19,510 --> 00:17:21,829
You want all of us to cut ties with you?

337
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:24,270
You must help us.

338
00:17:24,880 --> 00:17:26,750
Or I'll tell the entire class

339
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:29,400
that Yi Lan got good grades
because you tutored her.

340
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:31,160
I'll have everyone come to you for help.

341
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:31,680
Ditto.

342
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:32,640
Ditto.

343
00:17:37,030 --> 00:17:38,160
About this formula,

344
00:17:39,310 --> 00:17:40,720
I've basically explained everything.

345
00:17:40,720 --> 00:17:42,000
Is everyone clear on this?

346
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,270
Yes.

347
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:44,070
Yes.

348
00:17:44,790 --> 00:17:46,850
Math is different from liberal arts.

349
00:17:47,110 --> 00:17:48,240
You have to understand

350
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:49,680
the formula
instead of memorizing it by rote

351
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:50,920
or applying it mechanically.

352
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:52,000
Just like Mr. Bu says,

353
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:54,240
there's more than one solution
to a math problem.

354
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:55,500
Flexibility is a must.

355
00:17:57,240 --> 00:17:57,680
Yi Lan.

356
00:17:58,750 --> 00:18:00,270
Repeat my explanation.

357
00:18:03,310 --> 00:18:05,750
Well, I... got the gist.

358
00:18:06,070 --> 00:18:06,550
But...

359
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:07,510
Tong Xiaole!

360
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,260
Zhao Zhenghao.

361
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:11,810
What do you want?

362
00:18:16,940 --> 00:18:18,570
[Qingmu High School Final Test
for Grade 11 Students]

363
00:18:17,400 --> 00:18:18,550
Thirteen points?

364
00:18:21,160 --> 00:18:22,750
You must've written the answers
with all your heart,

365
00:18:22,750 --> 00:18:24,880
because even random scribbling
could've got you a higher score.

366
00:18:24,880 --> 00:18:26,480
This is too low a score.

367
00:18:30,030 --> 00:18:31,350
I'm an art student.

368
00:18:31,830 --> 00:18:34,090
My worth isn't measured by grades alone.

369
00:18:34,110 --> 00:18:35,880
I am very talented in art.

370
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:39,140
What are you trying to say?

371
00:18:41,030 --> 00:18:43,160
I've observed you guys for a long time.

372
00:18:45,030 --> 00:18:45,760
Tong Xiaole.

373
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:49,000
Let me join the group, will you?

374
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:51,000
I can be an assistant monitor to you.

375
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:52,720
Stay away from me.

376
00:18:54,790 --> 00:18:55,550
Tong Xiaole!

377
00:18:56,750 --> 00:18:57,550
Let go of me!

378
00:18:57,550 --> 00:18:58,510
My mom said

379
00:18:58,720 --> 00:18:59,920
if I failed another exam,

380
00:18:59,920 --> 00:19:01,240
she'd stop giving me my allowance.

381
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:03,160
Zhao Zhenghao, how is that relevant to me?

382
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:04,270
It's not about money.

383
00:19:04,270 --> 00:19:05,240
Stay away from me!

384
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:06,000
It's about my dignity.

385
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:06,880
I refuse!

386
00:19:06,880 --> 00:19:07,680
I can't lose my dignity!

387
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:09,440
Tong Xiaole, please, I beg you.

388
00:19:12,310 --> 00:19:13,070
Tong Xiaole.

389
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:23,600
Come on, have some fruit.

390
00:19:26,770 --> 00:19:29,180
[Study Plan by Mr. Tong]

391
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:29,140
Completed.

392
00:19:37,030 --> 00:19:38,490
It's time to watch dramas.

393
00:19:39,350 --> 00:19:40,080
Give it to me.

394
00:19:41,030 --> 00:19:43,490
Since we're all here to study
on the weekend,

395
00:19:43,510 --> 00:19:45,040
we should follow the rules.

396
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:46,310
Got it?

397
00:19:49,310 --> 00:19:50,240
Stop reading it.

398
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:54,000
I haven't finished the first...

399
00:19:56,680 --> 00:19:58,080
I've done all the papers.

400
00:20:01,070 --> 00:20:01,680
Xiaole,

401
00:20:01,960 --> 00:20:02,720
something

402
00:20:02,720 --> 00:20:04,050
doesn't seem fair to me.

403
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:05,080
What is it?

404
00:20:05,240 --> 00:20:06,240
Look at your home.

405
00:20:07,590 --> 00:20:09,680
So much stuff exclusive to Yi Lan.

406
00:20:10,240 --> 00:20:11,960
I'm your brother from another mother.

407
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:13,160
I want the same treatment.

408
00:20:13,160 --> 00:20:14,790
As you said, it's all exclusive to me.

409
00:20:14,790 --> 00:20:16,200
So only I can enjoy it.

410
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:17,590
You're not getting anything.

411
00:20:17,590 --> 00:20:18,650
Double standards.

412
00:20:18,880 --> 00:20:20,440
I don't care. My brain is a mess now.

413
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:21,310
I need a break.

414
00:20:21,550 --> 00:20:22,400
So do I.

415
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:24,270
We've barely started.

416
00:20:24,480 --> 00:20:25,750
Every minute counts.

417
00:20:26,510 --> 00:20:27,440
Let's continue.

418
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:56,400
Who...

419
00:20:56,720 --> 00:20:57,720
Who are you trying to scare

420
00:20:57,720 --> 00:20:58,880
with that stupid face of yours?

421
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:00,510
I don't have a stupid face.
But you do have a stupid brain!

422
00:21:00,510 --> 00:21:02,240
Who are you calling stupid?

423
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:04,160
You can solve a few math problems.
So what?

424
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:05,310
Gentlemen use words, and not fists.

425
00:21:05,310 --> 00:21:06,750
Don't push me any further!

426
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:08,720
I'm not pushing you!

427
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:09,790
Stop running!

428
00:21:09,790 --> 00:21:11,000
What are you doing?

429
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:14,240
Don't do that!

430
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:16,310
Let go of me!

431
00:21:18,170 --> 00:21:19,650
♪ I can see you once I open my eyes ♪

432
00:21:20,050 --> 00:21:21,720
♪ Silly me, can't help but gaze at you ♪

433
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,000
Stop butting in!

434
00:21:22,180 --> 00:21:25,040
♪ Your love is like a pink cloud ♪

435
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:24,000
Stay there, you!

436
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:28,750
Stop running. Who has a stupid brain now?
Who?

437
00:21:26,060 --> 00:21:27,710
♪ Whenever you come near ♪

438
00:21:27,770 --> 00:21:29,850
♪ I lose myself in you ♪

439
00:21:30,760 --> 00:21:33,820
♪ The corners of my mouth turn up
simply at the thought of you ♪

440
00:21:34,600 --> 00:21:36,120
♪ My IQ goes to zero ♪

441
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:37,980
♪ Calories are my only cure ♪

442
00:21:38,530 --> 00:21:41,690
♪ I want a cup of boba tea with sugar ♪

443
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:44,260
♪ With you around ♪

444
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:46,550
♪ I feel like an untethered wild horse ♪

445
00:21:47,200 --> 00:21:49,480
♪ Love is the reason for gaining weight ♪

446
00:21:50,560 --> 00:21:53,580
♪ Boba tea with sugar means I like you ♪

447
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:55,490
♪ Warm palms ♪

448
00:21:56,040 --> 00:21:57,620
♪ The pleasant smell of love ♪

449
00:21:57,980 --> 00:22:00,130
♪ I sync my playlist with yours
in secret ♪

450
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:59,030
Read carefully.

451
00:21:58,950 --> 00:22:00,160
[Final Exam]

452
00:21:59,200 --> 00:22:00,240
Good luck to you all.

453
00:22:00,240 --> 00:22:01,160
♪ Let our hearts beat in sync ♪

454
00:22:01,240 --> 00:22:02,510
♪ Let us breathe in sync ♪

455
00:22:03,140 --> 00:22:06,860
♪ I absolutely, totally,
and utterly adore you ♪

456
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:07,840
♪ Boba tea with sugar ♪

457
00:22:08,260 --> 00:22:09,870
♪ My dream for each new day ♪

458
00:22:08,350 --> 00:22:11,610
[Final Exam]

459
00:22:10,260 --> 00:22:11,870
♪ Is to hold you ♪

460
00:22:12,290 --> 00:22:13,830
♪ And have fun, hee-hee ♪

461
00:22:14,350 --> 00:22:15,580
♪ Without doubt ♪

462
00:22:15,630 --> 00:22:16,360
♪ The boba ♪

463
00:22:16,410 --> 00:22:17,580
♪ And pudding in my tea ♪

464
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:18,930
♪ Are all yours ♪

465
00:22:19,340 --> 00:22:22,080
♪ You are everything I want ♪

466
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:24,720
Chen Fan, scored 100 points. Gosh.
It's a triple digit.

467
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:26,510
For getting a triple digit
within such a short time,

468
00:22:26,510 --> 00:22:27,640
Chen Fan, you are...

469
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:29,550
a real genius.

470
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:32,960
Yi Lan,

471
00:22:33,200 --> 00:22:34,400
scored 105 points.

472
00:22:34,480 --> 00:22:36,960
It's my first time exceeding 100 points.
Great!

473
00:22:36,960 --> 00:22:38,790
Qiao Mengmeng, scored 125 points.

474
00:22:38,790 --> 00:22:41,640
A small effort has yielded a big return.

475
00:22:49,240 --> 00:22:51,030
Luo Ningzi, scored 145 points.

476
00:22:54,030 --> 00:22:56,000
Did you study even in your sleep?

477
00:22:57,000 --> 00:23:00,000
Actually, I think Xiaole's tutoring
was very helpful.

478
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:02,730
All I did was grasp the concepts
and extrapolate.

479
00:23:06,510 --> 00:23:08,640
Zhao Zhenghao is here to make a report.

480
00:23:09,750 --> 00:23:10,720
In this exam,

481
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:13,240
Zhao Zhenghao scored 91 points.

482
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:16,200
Nice work, Mr. Zhao.

483
00:23:16,640 --> 00:23:17,720
Please be seated!

484
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:28,270
As your tutor,
regarding your recent achievements

485
00:23:28,270 --> 00:23:29,480
I'm very gratified.

486
00:23:30,310 --> 00:23:32,510
Keep up the good work though, everyone.

487
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:37,960
Tong Xiaole scored a high score
of 150 points.

488
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:40,080
Do learn from him, all of you.

489
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:43,240
This is...

490
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:45,680
your last summer vacation at  high school.

491
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:47,000
I hope each of you will keep

492
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:48,730
studying during the holidays.

493
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:52,440
Get prepared
for the college entrance exam.

494
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:57,960
Mr. Chen,

495
00:23:58,200 --> 00:23:59,790
you have limitless potential.

496
00:23:59,790 --> 00:24:01,450
You must believe in yourself.

497
00:24:01,510 --> 00:24:02,750
All the effort you've put in

498
00:24:02,750 --> 00:24:05,080
will pay off in the college entrance exam.

499
00:24:05,240 --> 00:24:05,750
Yes!

500
00:24:06,920 --> 00:24:07,920
All rise!

501
00:24:09,960 --> 00:24:11,090
Thank you, Mr. Tong.

502
00:24:11,590 --> 00:24:13,990
-Thank you, Mr. Tong.
-Thank you, Mr. Tong.

503
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:15,690
Well then...

504
00:24:16,400 --> 00:24:17,200
you're welcome.

505
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:19,000
Sit or move around as you please.

506
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:19,750
Xiaole,

507
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:22,320
can I borrow your test paper?

508
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:22,920
Sure.

509
00:24:29,070 --> 00:24:29,960
Goodbye, Sir.

510
00:24:30,510 --> 00:24:31,240
Goodbye.

511
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:38,920
How was my acting? I want comments now.

512
00:24:38,920 --> 00:24:40,240
Alright. Now that the outsider's gone,

513
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:41,000
and Xiaole's done with the acting,

514
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,240
let's talk about the real business.

515
00:24:42,240 --> 00:24:43,270
After a rough week,

516
00:24:43,270 --> 00:24:45,720
don't you want to reward yourselves
properly?

517
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:46,270
Yes!

518
00:24:46,640 --> 00:24:49,000
How about we spend two days and a night
in the mountain villa

519
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:50,060
owned by my family?

520
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:51,240
Sounds lovely!

521
00:24:51,240 --> 00:24:52,480
Ning, come with us.

522
00:24:53,920 --> 00:24:56,240
I've signed up for specialized courses
and IELTS classes.

523
00:24:56,240 --> 00:24:57,680
I don't think I can make it this time.

524
00:24:57,680 --> 00:25:00,070
Then you won't have time
to practice the cello with me?

525
00:25:00,070 --> 00:25:00,480
Look,

526
00:25:00,750 --> 00:25:02,950
hire a tutor to train your skills first.

527
00:25:02,960 --> 00:25:04,820
I'm sure we can hang out sometime.

528
00:25:05,160 --> 00:25:06,160
Are you really not going?

529
00:25:06,160 --> 00:25:07,310
Are you really not going?

530
00:25:07,310 --> 00:25:08,640
Have loads of fun, guys.

531
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:11,160
Mr. Chen Fan!

532
00:25:11,480 --> 00:25:13,010
After all I've done for you,

533
00:25:13,160 --> 00:25:14,960
don't you owe me a proper praise?

534
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:17,720
You are amazing.

535
00:25:18,310 --> 00:25:19,240
Impressive.

536
00:25:19,240 --> 00:25:20,770
-Very much so.
-Marvelous.

537
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:24,920
In this final exam,

538
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:26,480
Lan's scores improved

539
00:25:26,750 --> 00:25:27,680
quite a lot.

540
00:25:27,790 --> 00:25:28,880
Good job, Sister.

541
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:30,030
Bravo.

542
00:25:31,240 --> 00:25:32,070
Let's celebrate.

543
00:25:32,070 --> 00:25:33,750
What's there to celebrate?

544
00:25:33,920 --> 00:25:35,240
It's not like I got the first place.

545
00:25:35,240 --> 00:25:37,480
But you will get there one day,
Sister.

546
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:39,000
That's right. Cheers.

547
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:40,000
Cheers.

548
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:48,400
That said, Lan, take my advice.

549
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:50,400
Don't stay up late to study anymore.

550
00:25:50,720 --> 00:25:51,880
It's bad for your health.

551
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:52,920
Okay. Got it.

552
00:25:53,270 --> 00:25:54,680
Nothing can't be done without health.

553
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:55,270
Yeah.

554
00:25:56,000 --> 00:25:56,400
Dad.

555
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:56,740
Yes?

556
00:25:56,750 --> 00:25:58,070
I have a little request.

557
00:25:58,070 --> 00:25:58,270
What is it?

558
00:25:58,270 --> 00:25:59,510
I'd like to have a two-day trip

559
00:25:59,510 --> 00:26:01,680
with Xiaole and some other classmates
this weekend.

560
00:26:01,680 --> 00:26:02,140
Can I go?

561
00:26:03,000 --> 00:26:03,640
With Xiaole?

562
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:04,160
Yes.

563
00:26:04,160 --> 00:26:04,790
You can go.

564
00:26:04,880 --> 00:26:05,210
Sure.

565
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:07,030
But you must stay safe.

566
00:26:07,240 --> 00:26:07,510
Yes.

567
00:26:07,510 --> 00:26:08,040
Alright?

568
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:11,080
Dad, I have one more request.

569
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:13,440
Can't you say them all at once?

570
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:15,170
Speak up.

571
00:26:17,440 --> 00:26:20,200
I'd like to attend
professional cello lessons.

572
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:20,920
No.

573
00:26:26,310 --> 00:26:26,960
Lan,

574
00:26:29,480 --> 00:26:30,240
I hope

575
00:26:30,880 --> 00:26:32,610
you will get into a university.

576
00:26:32,960 --> 00:26:33,480
Well,

577
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:34,960
not necessarily a great one.

578
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:35,920
An ordinary one is fine.

579
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,830
You keep saying that all the time.

580
00:26:38,030 --> 00:26:39,000
If my mom were still around,

581
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:40,860
she would definitely support me.

582
00:26:41,350 --> 00:26:43,350
Dad, don't you bully my sister!

583
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:45,080
Just eat. Don't chime in.

584
00:26:47,310 --> 00:26:48,160
Lan,

585
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:49,310
can we put

586
00:26:49,720 --> 00:26:50,650
this discussion

587
00:26:51,240 --> 00:26:52,270
on hold?

588
00:26:53,310 --> 00:26:54,960
We'll talk later. Let's eat.

589
00:26:56,510 --> 00:26:57,310
Come on.

590
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:59,320
Look at this, a gift from Mom.

591
00:27:00,550 --> 00:27:01,480
Guess what it is.

592
00:27:03,310 --> 00:27:04,200
I don't know.

593
00:27:04,480 --> 00:27:06,270
It's a cello. Care for a try?

594
00:27:06,480 --> 00:27:06,960
Sure.

595
00:27:07,070 --> 00:27:07,670
Come here.

596
00:27:07,790 --> 00:27:08,680
This is the bow.

597
00:27:09,480 --> 00:27:11,080
Hold it with your right hand.

598
00:27:13,240 --> 00:27:14,550
Just hold the bow

599
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:16,310
like you're holding an egg.

600
00:27:16,310 --> 00:27:17,200
Put it here?

601
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:18,130
Yes, right here.

602
00:27:18,830 --> 00:27:20,890
Now, draw the bow across the strings.

603
00:27:22,480 --> 00:27:23,440
Does it sound good?

604
00:27:23,440 --> 00:27:23,920
Yes.

605
00:27:23,960 --> 00:27:24,620
Great, huh?

606
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:26,600
A big bite.

607
00:27:27,480 --> 00:27:30,200
You can write down your wishes
on the candy wrapper, Lan.

608
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:34,240
I wish to celebrate my birthday tomorrow
with Mom.

609
00:27:34,480 --> 00:27:35,480
Birthday celebration, huh?

610
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:35,790
Yeah.

611
00:27:35,790 --> 00:27:37,990
Of course. I'll always be there for you.

612
00:28:05,070 --> 00:28:05,510
Hmm.

613
00:28:06,510 --> 00:28:07,970
Your dream will come true.

614
00:28:12,270 --> 00:28:13,600
Are you feeling better?

615
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:16,170
Let's go.

616
00:28:16,750 --> 00:28:17,270
No.

617
00:28:18,030 --> 00:28:20,090
I'd like to hang around here for a bit.

618
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:21,480
Here?

619
00:28:24,030 --> 00:28:25,030
Then give me a smile.

620
00:28:25,030 --> 00:28:27,760
I'll consider whether to keep you company
or not.

621
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:30,790
Watch this.

622
00:28:38,550 --> 00:28:39,240
Hold on!

623
00:28:42,670 --> 00:28:45,990
[Purple-spotted Tonguefish]

624
00:28:43,880 --> 00:28:45,030
Read these characters.

625
00:28:43,910 --> 00:28:46,810
♪ Dusk gently fell on the coastline ♪

626
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:48,310
"Purple-spotted..."

627
00:28:47,570 --> 00:28:50,460
♪ The quietly passing breeze
gave the clouds a kiss ♪

628
00:28:49,240 --> 00:28:50,550
Then it's...

629
00:28:51,140 --> 00:28:54,470
♪ The revolving earth
was bathed in romantic colors ♪

630
00:28:51,680 --> 00:28:52,720
It's...

631
00:28:54,590 --> 00:28:57,490
♪ That was the moment I met you ♪

632
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:58,720
Gunpowder loaded.

633
00:28:57,970 --> 00:29:00,790
♪ Even mountains and seas
can't separate us ♪

634
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:00,480
Three.

635
00:29:00,480 --> 00:29:01,000
Two.

636
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:01,400
One.

637
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:02,270
Launch!

638
00:29:01,630 --> 00:29:04,080
♪ I wish I could turn into a bird
to explore the world for you ♪

639
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:04,200
What a long slide!

640
00:29:04,480 --> 00:29:06,240
It's so fun. Come down here now!

641
00:29:04,870 --> 00:29:08,040
♪ The vast galaxy is singing
tender songs ♪

642
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:07,000
Here I come!

643
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:08,160
Hurry!

644
00:29:08,510 --> 00:29:11,100
♪ I can't live a second without you ♪

645
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:12,510
One more slide.

646
00:29:11,810 --> 00:29:14,970
♪ Looking forward
to the next beautiful dream ♪

647
00:29:15,270 --> 00:29:19,620
♪ I want to see every romantic sky
with you ♪

648
00:29:16,210 --> 00:29:19,180
[REC]

649
00:29:19,480 --> 00:29:20,960
My butt!

650
00:29:20,110 --> 00:29:24,130
♪ The evening breeze tells
heartfelt emotions ♪

651
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:23,460
Why are you still filming?

652
00:29:25,050 --> 00:29:28,370
♪ Stars surround you and smile at you ♪

653
00:29:26,070 --> 00:29:27,130
Where's my camera?

654
00:29:27,550 --> 00:29:28,720
Where did it go?

655
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:31,540
♪ I give you all the good things
in the world ♪

656
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:29,480
My cam...

657
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:31,160
Stop filming me.

658
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:33,110
Photographers never get in the frame!

659
00:29:31,770 --> 00:29:35,650
♪ The light in your eyes shines
like diamonds ♪

660
00:29:33,480 --> 00:29:34,440
Turn it off!

661
00:29:35,920 --> 00:29:36,880
This is annoying!

662
00:29:35,930 --> 00:29:38,850
♪ Drawing an exclamation mark
in my world ♪

663
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:42,170
♪ The night breeze embraces you
while I run towards you ♪

664
00:29:42,070 --> 00:29:43,070
It's pretty!

665
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:45,140
♪ I hear our passionate heartbeats ♪

666
00:29:45,750 --> 00:29:49,540
♪ Let's build a castle in a dream ♪

667
00:29:49,860 --> 00:29:52,160
♪ Every star is a romantic symbol ♪

668
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:55,880
Yi Lan will definitely become a cellist!

669
00:29:52,270 --> 00:29:55,310
♪ Let me find you ♪

670
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:58,920
Yes, I will!

671
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:01,750
Then what should Tong Xiaole do?

672
00:30:02,920 --> 00:30:05,160
Ask yourself!

673
00:30:19,350 --> 00:30:20,110
I'm back.

674
00:30:21,200 --> 00:30:22,480
You're back, Sister!

675
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:24,480
Kiddo,

676
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:26,160
did you behave at school today?

677
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:27,160
Yes, I did!

678
00:30:27,160 --> 00:30:28,070
I doubt it.

679
00:30:28,400 --> 00:30:29,530
Then ask my teacher.

680
00:30:30,750 --> 00:30:31,550
Auntie.

681
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:33,680
Hello.

682
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:39,310
You were adorable.

683
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:41,480
Am I not adorable now?

684
00:30:41,550 --> 00:30:43,640
Yes, you are. Pretty, too.

685
00:30:45,960 --> 00:30:47,420
Xiaole was also adorable.

686
00:30:50,240 --> 00:30:53,110
Why are there so many photos of Xiaole
in your album?

687
00:30:53,310 --> 00:30:55,110
I've known him since childhood.

688
00:30:56,720 --> 00:30:57,510
That's true.

689
00:31:00,550 --> 00:31:02,110
Your mother was gorgeous.

690
00:31:03,200 --> 00:31:05,270
Not only that, she was also amazing,

691
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:08,030
as the principal player
of a major cello orchestra.

692
00:31:08,030 --> 00:31:09,890
She took me with her on every tour.

693
00:31:10,200 --> 00:31:11,640
Your mom was incredible.

694
00:31:12,070 --> 00:31:13,600
What did she see in your dad?

695
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:16,000
I'm not suggesting that he's awful.

696
00:31:16,030 --> 00:31:19,550
But didn't you always complain
him being stingy and naggy?

697
00:31:20,110 --> 00:31:22,070
My dad is a considerate gentleman.

698
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:24,460
He makes delicious food for us every day.

699
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:28,210
What do you think of this dress?

700
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:35,440
Replace it with this.

701
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:43,800
That's it.

702
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:49,560
This outfit and skirt...

703
00:31:50,070 --> 00:31:52,350
I'd like to wear these
to my idol's concert.

704
00:31:52,350 --> 00:31:53,270
Okay. I'll lend them to you.

705
00:31:53,270 --> 00:31:53,730
Thanks.

706
00:31:58,070 --> 00:31:59,400
Have some fruit, girls.

707
00:32:02,590 --> 00:32:04,440
Mengmeng, why not stay for dinner?

708
00:32:04,440 --> 00:32:05,640
No, thanks, Mrs. Yi.

709
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:06,200
Alright.

710
00:32:06,200 --> 00:32:07,130
Thanks, Auntie.

711
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:10,030
Eat up!

712
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:14,000
How are things

713
00:32:14,920 --> 00:32:15,580
between you

714
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:17,080
and your stepmother?

715
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:18,750
Well...

716
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:20,810
Generally fine.

717
00:32:21,720 --> 00:32:23,240
Do you still miss your mom?

718
00:32:23,480 --> 00:32:24,510
Of course I do!

719
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:26,510
I thought so.

720
00:32:27,960 --> 00:32:29,480
Sometimes, I think

721
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:31,730
if my mom were still around,

722
00:32:32,240 --> 00:32:34,000
she would definitely be my tutor

723
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:36,530
and shape me into a great cellist
like she was.

724
00:32:37,270 --> 00:32:38,000
Wait.

725
00:32:38,510 --> 00:32:42,040
Your dad shouldn't be against
you practicing the cello, right?

726
00:32:42,440 --> 00:32:43,640
I don't get it either.

727
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:45,130
Every time I mention

728
00:32:45,160 --> 00:32:45,790
the cello,

729
00:32:46,030 --> 00:32:47,760
he gets really stern and weird.

730
00:32:48,550 --> 00:32:49,480
Perhaps...

731
00:32:50,480 --> 00:32:52,810
me playing the cello
reminds him of my mom.

732
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:53,790
Hmm.

733
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:56,720
I miss my dad too.

734
00:32:57,310 --> 00:32:58,170
But as you know,

735
00:32:58,240 --> 00:32:59,920
my mom never agrees to let me see him,

736
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:01,720
accusing him of being a scumbag.

737
00:33:02,270 --> 00:33:04,800
I definitely won't find a boyfriend
like him.

738
00:33:06,240 --> 00:33:08,240
I'm determined to be with someone

739
00:33:08,270 --> 00:33:11,200
who will treat me very, very well.

740
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:12,720
I believe you'll find that guy.

741
00:33:12,720 --> 00:33:14,980
Don't forget that I'll keep you company.

742
00:33:18,480 --> 00:33:19,550
So beautiful!

743
00:33:26,640 --> 00:33:28,480
Xiaole, take photos of me instead!

744
00:33:28,480 --> 00:33:29,280
That's right!

745
00:33:42,200 --> 00:33:43,260
You all look great.

746
00:33:49,630 --> 00:33:52,850
[REC]

747
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:03,880
Look, a goose!

748
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:06,480
And it's black.

749
00:34:07,550 --> 00:34:08,510
So pretty.

750
00:34:10,630 --> 00:34:11,920
Shall we go take some photos?

751
00:34:11,920 --> 00:34:12,780
Sure, let's go.

752
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:13,260
Xiaole!

753
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:14,540
Give me the camera.

754
00:34:15,510 --> 00:34:16,670
Be careful. Don't drop it.

755
00:34:16,670 --> 00:34:17,469
Rest assured.

756
00:34:23,630 --> 00:34:24,830
It's beautiful here.

757
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:26,760
Let me take a photo of you. Hurry!

758
00:34:27,070 --> 00:34:27,670
Next pose.

759
00:34:28,840 --> 00:34:29,170
Next.

760
00:34:29,480 --> 00:34:29,880
Next.

761
00:34:30,150 --> 00:34:30,480
Good.

762
00:34:31,030 --> 00:34:31,400
Good.

763
00:34:32,400 --> 00:34:32,800
Great.

764
00:34:32,840 --> 00:34:33,280
Next pose.

765
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:33,510
Done.

766
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:33,969
My turn!

767
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:53,730
Anything wrong?

768
00:34:56,510 --> 00:34:57,590
Well...

769
00:34:57,880 --> 00:35:00,140
I'm just thinking about my mother again.

770
00:35:01,670 --> 00:35:03,320
She told me

771
00:35:04,480 --> 00:35:07,340
when I reached a certain level
at playing the cello,

772
00:35:07,630 --> 00:35:09,290
I could feel a flow in my heart.

773
00:35:10,920 --> 00:35:13,510
Actually, I've always been curious

774
00:35:15,070 --> 00:35:16,550
how that flow would feel

775
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:19,320
when I play the cello.

776
00:35:32,480 --> 00:35:34,320
You're terrible at it.

777
00:35:34,670 --> 00:35:38,510
Don't play the cello again.

778
00:35:44,960 --> 00:35:46,360
What are you laughing at?

779
00:35:48,110 --> 00:35:49,280
I don't know

780
00:35:49,550 --> 00:35:52,070
what the flow you're talking about
feels like.

781
00:35:52,070 --> 00:35:54,150
But I did feel tears running down my face

782
00:35:54,150 --> 00:35:56,000
the first time I heard you play the cello.

783
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:57,860
Can't you just drop that subject?

784
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:59,440
I remember you played the cello

785
00:35:59,440 --> 00:36:01,100
like you were sawing firwood.

786
00:36:02,670 --> 00:36:04,440
You're asking for a beating!

787
00:36:05,360 --> 00:36:07,550
Mengmeng, Chen Fan, come here!

788
00:36:07,550 --> 00:36:09,150
Someone's getting annoying again!

789
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:10,070
We're coming!

790
00:36:11,510 --> 00:36:12,310
Come here now!

791
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:17,030
Look.

792
00:36:17,030 --> 00:36:17,800
Take a look.

793
00:36:20,590 --> 00:36:21,840
Such lovely photos.

794
00:36:23,630 --> 00:36:24,960
Take a group photo of us,

795
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:27,120
including yourself.

796
00:36:34,840 --> 00:36:35,840
Chen Fan,

797
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:38,550
how much longer
until we get to your house?

798
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:42,670
Very soon.

799
00:36:44,510 --> 00:36:49,910
[I hope Dad will stop objecting
to me learning the cello]
[It will come true]
